  "title": "Therapy Assistant (office hours, 5 days) #HAC",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Scope:</strong></p><ul><li>Provide personalize restorative care to clients according to clients’ care plans</li><li>Conduct group activities (which includes: exercise groups, cognitive groups, leisure groups)</li><li>Provide individual maintenance rehab for clients</li><li>Assist therapists during rehab sessions</li><li>Prepare inventory list of equipment and supplies; perform regular inventory checks and equipment maintenance</li><li>Set-up treatment areas and equipment</li><li>Ensure treatment rooms are neat and clean</li><li>Assist in simple administrative matters</li><li>Participate in company’s outreach events, community mobility and outings when required</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Min Nitec and above </li><li>WSQ Certificate in Therapy Support (Good to have)</li><li>Able to start immediately </li></ul><p><strong>Interested candidates please send your resume to anna.chen@recruitexpress.com.sg </strong><br /><strong></strong></p><p>Anna Chen jiaxin</p><p>CEI No: R25157621</p><p>Recruit Express Pte Ltd  </p><p>EA License: 99C4599</p>",
